{"tid":25471,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人覺得合味道冬蔭功味難左好撚多","createTime":"2016-12-06T06:46:04.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-06T14:45:31.000Z","uid":55514,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"bdf692adbe8b52d2d5a6921204148a507dec0a00","tid":25471,"uid":55514,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T06:46:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://holland.pk/bmx56h2q\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fbmx56h2q&h=7967af5b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n我就廢J唔係咁食得辣嘅<br />\n但平時都中意食泰國餐廳果啲冬蔭功，而且頂得順<br />\n咁好耐之前就合味道就出左隻冬蔭功味啦<br />\n我就迫不及待想試試<br />\n一開始覺得唔係咁辣，又有冬蔭功果種酸，勁撚正，差唔多兩個星期食一次咁制<br />\n咁之後停左一排<br />\n今日朝早見屋企有咪諗住食<br />\n一食<br />\n屌辣撚到仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，又冇左浸酸味，得個辣<br />\n真心覺得以前嘅高質啲<br />\n依家係咪轉左配方?"},{"pid":"7703e1d5644a079f637825972341a1b0ddaa018b","tid":25471,"uid":1977,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T06:56:28.000Z","msg":"yes 以前一直都拎A<br />\n而家最多都係C+"},{"pid":"32885f73b6f9c442cad873d0c8610838d0b9f22b","tid":25471,"uid":55514,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T10:34:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>yes 以前一直都拎A<br />\n而家最多都係C+</blockquote><br />\nf都唔知有冇"},{"pid":"02e7e22fd071c472a42827901e8a970a3d04f501","tid":25471,"uid":55514,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T10:35:09.000Z","msg":"留名"},{"pid":"43e6349dcf4f3b422ecf45bcc39720a397f00fe2","tid":25471,"uid":10089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T10:36:25.000Z","msg":"有冇人覺得合味道<del>冬蔭功味</del>難左好撚多"},{"pid":"de2fca547d6d684ad242454a1967d4fda2459b50","tid":25471,"uid":55514,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T14:45:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有冇人覺得合味道<del>冬蔭功味</del>難左好撚多</blockquote><br />\n海鮮都唔差丫"}]}